  "text": "All experiments are performed on the widely used Pascal VOC dataset [CITATION_1] . We train our models on the Pascal VOC 07 and VOC 12 trainval sets and test them on the VOC 07 test set. Performance is measured in AP 50 which is AP computed for bounding boxes with at least 50% intersection-over-union overlap with any of the ground truth bounding boxes.",
